last_episode_to_air.name: Say Goodbye to Hollywood (2)
last_episode_to_air.overview: As the ground rumbles beneath LA, the Spy Racer family comes together one last time to end Dann's reign and make their hometown safe again.

name: Fast & Furious Spy Racers
overview: A government agency recruits teen driver Tony Toretto and his thrill-seeking friends to infiltrate a criminal street racing circuit as undercover spies.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Tony Toretto, Dominic Toretto's cousin, is recruited by a government agency together with his friends to infiltrate an elite racing league serving as a front for a crime organization called SH1FT3R that is bent on world domination.

seasons.name: Season 2: Rio
seasons.overview: When one of their own goes missing, the Spy Racers must leave LA and head to Brazil to take down a crime organization in Rio.

seasons.name: Season 3: Sahara
seasons.overview: Faced with their toughest mission yet in the remote Sahara, the Spy Racers head into danger to prove they're more than a team — they’re a family.

seasons.name: Season 4: Mexico
seasons.overview: When the Spy Racers are framed for a crime they didn't commit, they flee to Mexico to clear their name and uncover a new evil scheme.

seasons.name: Season 5: South Pacific
seasons.overview: One of the Spy Racers has been captured by an old foe, leading the rest of the crew on a far-flung rescue mission... in the South Pacific!

seasons.name: Season 6: Homecoming
seasons.overview: The final season takes the Spy Racers around the world — from the Alps to the Arctic and back home to LA — as they battle their toughest enemy ever!

episodes.name: Born a Toretto
episodes.overview: Tony is pumped when his legendary cousin Dom recruits him and his friends for an exciting mission: to infiltrate a secret street racing circuit.

episodes.name: Enter SH1FT3R
episodes.overview: After Tony rocks it against Layla in a thrilling race through LA, SH1FT3R boss Shashi invites Tony's crew to join his group by pulling a job for him.

episodes.name: Ghost Town Grand Prix
episodes.overview: Tony takes on all the SH1FT3R racers in a remote ghost town. But Tony's real mission isn’t to win -- it's to track what scheme Shashi's up to.

episodes.name: The Owl Job
episodes.overview: While Tony works with Layla and Shashi to steal codes from a Russian businessman, Ms. Nowhere sends the others to snoop around Shashi's mansion.

episodes.name: The Celestial Vault
episodes.overview: The crew enters a SH1FT3R race up a privately owned mountain. Can they find out what Shashi wants at the summit without blowing their cover?

episodes.name: The Final Key
episodes.overview: Ms. Nowhere tells the crew that the mission is over, but Tony isn't ready to give up. He's too much of a Toretto to back off now.

episodes.name: Ignition
episodes.overview: When the crew takes over an amazing spy plane, they meet Shashi in the desert to exchange precious cargo. Will they also learn Shashi's master plan?

episodes.name: The Key to the Strip
episodes.overview: It's up to Tony and his crew to save the world when Shashi sets up a showdown with evil billionaire Cleve Kelso on the Las Vegas strip.

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: Tony Toretto, Dominic Toretto's cousin, is recruited by a government agency together with his friends to infiltrate an elite racing league serving as a front for a crime organization called SH1FT3R that is bent on world domination.

episodes.name: Escape from L.A.
episodes.overview: When the Spy Racers make a big bust in LA, they learn about a secret operation in Brazil and plead with Ms. Nowhere to let them go undercover.

episodes.name: That Sinking Feeling
episodes.overview: After arriving in Brazil, the crew gets their ride stuck in quicksand. But Tony's determined to get them out of trouble without Ms. Nowhere’s help.

episodes.name: Bem-vindo ao Rio
episodes.overview: The Spy Racers explore Rio hoping to find the gang that captured Layla, but soon have to question if she’s on their side or has turned against them.

episodes.name: Combustion
episodes.overview: After Frostee discovers that the secret formula is explosive, Tony and Echo go into overdrive to find a tanker full of it before it blows up Rio.

episodes.name: Driving Blind
episodes.overview: An old friend helps the team figure out who’s behind the evil plan, then makes a shocking discovery after a hair-raising race in the streets.

episodes.name: An Echo of Nowhere
episodes.overview: On a dangerous mission to recover the hauler, Echo has to think quick on her feet to avoid capture by a surprising enemy.

episodes.name: The Patroness
episodes.overview: As a plan comes together to unleash the formula on an unsuspecting public, the Spy Racers scramble to stop it.

episodes.name: Tchau, Uggos
episodes.overview: With an angry mob on their tail, the team must pull out all the stops to recover the spy plane and save the world from a chilling reign of terror.

2.name: Season 2: Rio
2.overview: When one of their own goes missing, the Spy Racers must leave LA and head to Brazil to take down a crime organization in Rio.

episodes.name: The Giant Haboob
episodes.overview: Tony can't figure out why Echo was picked over him for spy school. Ms. Nowhere and Gary pursue a trio of familiar villains in Africa.

episodes.name: The Dead End
episodes.overview: Echo leads the Spy Racers to the Sahara to find Cleve Kelso, but when they're all captured, Layla and Tony must win a dune buggy race for their freedom.

episodes.name: The Empty Well
episodes.overview: The Spy Racers help a village with a water well that's run dry. Meanwhile, Ms. Nowhere and Gary try to make contact from the middle of... nowhere.

episodes.name: The Hunt
episodes.overview: With Kelso's lair in their sights, the team gets dragged into an epic dune buggy chase through the desert. Layla clashes with an old enemy.

episodes.name: The Bedouin Shield
episodes.overview: A hurricane in the Sahara? The team finds shelter with a group of Bedouins to escape a storm's wrath. Ms. Nowhere and Gary make an unexpected discovery.

episodes.name: The Eye of the Sahara
episodes.overview: As Kelso closes in on his evil goals, the Spy Racers face a tough decision in the remote desert. Will they follow their heads or their hearts?

episodes.name: RoboCleve
episodes.overview: Minus one key member, the team makes a final push to infiltrate Kelso's base to stop him from unleashing his diabolical plan.

episodes.name: Sirocco Fire Explosion
episodes.overview: The showdown in the Sahara comes to a fiery end when a swirling megastorm threatens to take out everything in its path — including the Spy Racers.

3.name: Season 3: Sahara
3.overview: Faced with their toughest mission yet in the remote Sahara, the Spy Racers head into danger to prove they're more than a team — they’re a family.

episodes.name: Chasing Phantoms
episodes.overview: Ms. Nowhere is rewarded with a party at headquarters when a worldwide chase leads to a big capture. But the celebration may be short-lived.

episodes.name: The Convoy
episodes.overview: Frostee works to bring Ms. Nowhere and the Spy Racers to safety. And now that the agency had turned on all of them, it's time to go rogue.

episodes.name: The Fugitives
episodes.overview: On the run and facing a shortage of money, the crew turns to what they do best — racing! — to earn enough cash to get them to Mexico City.

episodes.name: That's a Moray
episodes.overview: Ms. Nowhere and the Spy Racers crash a masquerade ball in Mexico City when stolen artifacts clue them in about who might have framed them.

episodes.name: The Ocelot King vs. El Mariposa
episodes.overview: As Ms. Nowhere and Echo confront Palindrome, Cisco tracks down Tuco in the wrestling ring, and Layla tells Frostee she feels unwanted on the team.

episodes.name: The Siege
episodes.overview: Trapped inside a hauler, the whole crew needs help as the authorities close in on them — and their hopes may rest on the newest member of the family.

episodes.name: Into the Labyrinth
episodes.overview: The Spy Racers are once again racing against the clock, this time to stop Mexico City from being destroyed by Moray's fiery volcano machine!

episodes.name: Don't Go Chasing Lavafalls
episodes.overview: Deep in lava-filled tunnels under the city, the Spy Racers make one last stand against Moray to stop his evil plan once and for all.

4.name: Season 4: Mexico
4.overview: When the Spy Racers are framed for a crime they didn't commit, they flee to Mexico to clear their name and uncover a new evil scheme.

episodes.name: R.O.A.M. Around the World
episodes.overview: The Spy Racers get caught up in playing a new virtual reality video game. But fun turns into frustration when Tony doesn't act like a good teammate.

episodes.name: The Rescue
episodes.overview: With one of their own in danger at the hands of their old enemy Sudarikov, the Spy Racers take to the sky for a daring aerial rescue.

episodes.name: Anchors Away
episodes.overview: From high in the sky to deep in the water! With a barrage of torpedoes on their tail, can the Spy Racers engineer an undersea escape?

episodes.name: Driving and Crying
episodes.overview: Stranded on an island in the South Pacific, the team plots its next move while trying to help Tony overcome his mysterious inability to drive.

episodes.name: Ride and Die
episodes.overview: Ms. Nowhere believes Shashi holds the information the team needs, so she agrees to free him for a day — even though the others doubt he can be trusted.

episodes.name: Ex Machina
episodes.overview: Layla, Tony and Shashi attempt to infiltrate Sudarikov’s island base. Elsewhere, the others struggle to rein in their out-of-control spy plane.

episodes.name: The Takeover
episodes.overview: The team finally gets into Sudarikov's underwater compound and must pull out all the stops to get the base shut down before disaster strikes.

episodes.name: The Toretto Virus
episodes.overview: To stop the virus from taking over the world, the Spy Racers will have to come together as a family to battle the most familiar foe they’ve ever faced.

5.name: Season 5: South Pacific
5.overview: One of the Spy Racers has been captured by an old foe, leading the rest of the crew on a far-flung rescue mission... in the South Pacific!

episodes.name: Incineration Day
episodes.overview: The stressed-out Spy Racers hope to blow off some steam — and blow up some stuff — on the agency’s "Incineration Day." But their fun will be short-lived.

episodes.name: Snowed In
episodes.overview: The team follows the person behind the Incineration Day incident all the way to the Alps, but is their prime suspect a mastermind or a pawn?

episodes.name: Rafaela's Raf-venge
episodes.overview: When Rafaela busts out of prison and starts causing trouble in Berlin, the team aims to shut her down to find out if she's behind the stolen spy tech.

episodes.name: Fun on the Autobahn
episodes.overview: Frostee becomes convinced that someone very close to him is behind the spy tech theft, and it leads to another high-speed chase on the Autobahn!

episodes.name: Detonation
episodes.overview: A member of the team has been kidnapped and taken to the Arctic, but Tony and Echo don’t see eye to eye on the best plan to get their friend back safely.

episodes.name: Meltdown
episodes.overview: Racing against the clock, the Spy Racers must disarm a weapon designed to melt the polar ice caps and leave much of the world underwater.

episodes.name: Hollywood Beginning
episodes.overview: The Spy Racers are getting comfortable with their return to civilian life at home, but Tony is obsessed with the notion that Dann is still out there.

episodes.name: Dann Hunt
episodes.overview: With the team unofficially back together, they hope to bring Nowhere and Palindrome back into the fold. Echo and Tony pay a visit to Matsuo.

episodes.name: Wildcat
episodes.overview: As Dann works to collect more of the devices she needs to execute her plan, the team drops in on a familiar face who becomes an unexpected ally.

episodes.name: Oil and Water
episodes.overview: The Spy Racers call in some old friends — and foes — to battle with Dann at an oil refinery and try to take her down to save LA.

episodes.name: Say Goodbye to Hollywood (1)
episodes.overview: When everyone gathers to attend a big movie premiere, Tony thinks about his life after the Spy Racers. But the team's last mission isn't over yet.

episodes.name: Say Goodbye to Hollywood (2)
episodes.overview: As the ground rumbles beneath LA, the Spy Racer family comes together one last time to end Dann's reign and make their hometown safe again.

6.name: Season 6: Homecoming
6.overview: The final season takes the Spy Racers around the world — from the Alps to the Arctic and back home to LA — as they battle their toughest enemy ever!
